b/Geometry/Manifold/ChartedSpace.html#ChartedSpace\">ChartedSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/ChartedSpace.html#ModelProd\">ModelProd</a> <span class=\"fn\">H</span> <span class=\"fn\">H'</span>)</span> (<span class=\"fn\">M</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\">M'</span>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The product of two charted spaces is naturally a charted space, with the canonical\nconstruction of the atlas of product maps. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/ChartedSpace.html#prodChartedSpace","kind":"instance","line":431,"name":"prodChartedSpace","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/ChartedSpace.lean#L431-L439"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/ChartedSpace.html#instTopologicalSpaceModelPi\"><span class=\"name\">instTopologicalSpaceModelPi</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ι</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_5}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Hi</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">ι</span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_6</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">Hi</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#Topo