b/Geometry/Manifold/ChartedSpace.html#ChartedSpace\"><span class=\"name\">ChartedSpace</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">H</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_5)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">H</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_6)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> (max u_5 u_6)</div></div>","info":{"doc":"A charted space is a topological space endowed with an atlas, i.e., a set of local\nhomeomorphisms taking values in a model space `H`, called charts, such that the domains of the\ncharts cover the whole space. We express the covering property by choosing for each `x` a member\n`chartAt x` of the atlas containing `x` in its source: in the smooth case, this is convenient to\nconstruct the tangent bundle in an efficient way.\nThe model space is written as an explicit parameter as there can be several model spaces for a\ngiven topological space. For instance, a complex manifold (modelled over `ℂ^n`) will also be seen\nsometimes as a real manifold over `ℝ^(2n)`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/ChartedSpace.html#ChartedSpace","kind":"class","line":128,"name":"ChartedSpace","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/ChartedSpace.lean#L128-L144"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Geometry.Manifold.StructureGroupoid","Mathlib.Topology.Connected.LocPathConnected","Mathlib.Topology.OpenPartialHomeomorph.Constructions"],"instances":[{"className":"ChartedSpace","name":"chartedSpaceSelf","typeNames":[]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"modelProdInhabited","typeNames":["ModelProd"]},{"className":"TopologicalSpace","name":"instTopologicalSpaceModelProd","typeNames":["ModelProd"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"modelPiInhabited","typeNames":["ModelPi"]},{"className":"TopologicalSpace","name":"instTopologicalSpaceModelPi","typeNames":["ModelPi"]},{"className":"ChartedSpace","name":"prodChartedSpace","typeNames":["ModelProd","Prod"]},{"className":"ChartedSpace","name":"piChartedSpace","typeNames":["ModelPi"]},{"className":"ChartedSpace","name":"ChartedSpace.sum","typeNames":["Sum"]}],"name":"Mathlib.Geometry.Manifold.ChartedSpace"}